This is how to circular_shift of x and shift:
   Remember that s is tostring of x
   Remember that n is s's length
   When n is 0, then:
      The answer is s
   End when
   Remember that k is remainder of shift and n
   Remember that result is ""
   Remember that i is k
   Do this diff of n and k times:
      Add result to item i in s
      Increase i
   End do
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this k times:
      Add result to item i in s
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know